  <name>Envelope</name>
  <summary>Personal budget application for the Elementary OS desktop</summary>

  <description>
    <p>Envelope helps you maintain your personal budget by using the tried-and-true [envelope system](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Envelope_system).</p>
    <p>You designate spending categories (envelopes) and distribute your monthly income into them.</p>
    <p>Envelope lets you configure accounts where you record all your transactions. You then assign each of them to a category.</p>
    <p>Originaly made by Nicolas Laplante<br/></p>
    <p>Features</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Envelope system budget workflow</li>
      <li>Import transactions from QIF/OFX files</li>
      <li>Integrates with the Elementary OS desktop</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <provides>
    <binary>com.github.cjfloss.envelope</binary>
  </provides>

  <screenshots>
    <screenshot type="default">
      <image>https://raw.githubusercontent.com/cjfloss/envelope/img/screenshot/1.png</image>
    </screenshot>
  </screenshots>

